Nipovaa Home VPN

Private VPN stack powered by:
- OpenVPN
- WireGuard
- dnsmasq
-Fail2ban
-UFW Firewall

## Quick install
'''bash
sudo bash vpn-server/install.sh

Start Services
Bash:
sudo bash vpn-server/start.sh
Stop Services
Bash:
sudo bash vpn-server/stop.sh

---
# vpn-server/install.sh
'''bash
#:/bin/bash

apt update
apt install openvpn easy-rsa wireguard
dnsmasq ufw fail2ban curl -y
echo "net.ipv4.ip_forward=1" >> /etc/
sysctl.conf
sysctl -p

systemctl enable openvpn
systemctl enable wg-quick@wg0
systemctl enable dnsmasq
systemctl enable fail2ban
echo "installation complete".
